
General
-------
- Win32 support. Hopefully we can use the EAWebKit version that SimCity proper uses. However, there are several necessary functions missing. I think these must be statically linked to SimCity.exe, along with EAIO, EASTL, etc. Thank you Maxis for this wonderful code organization. This is also why we're using Win32 and not Win64.
- GitHub releases. The aforementioned could be the major milestone to track 1.0
- Meanwhile, prereleases could be made if enough of the other things in this list get done.

